| Voice cloning accuracy for obscure figures | Acoustic design mode + voice actor licensing marketplace |
| Anthropomorphism subjectivity | Trait priority sliders, style presets, user override tools |
| Compute cost | Tiered rendering, local preview mode, cloud GPU auto-scaling + caching |

